social_posts.post_text:
excited to announce I’ve signed with adidas golf! happy to take this next step in my golf career & continue growing the game with such an iconic brand.///

📸: @golfinyourstate

Our Dulcedo Sports and Entertainment division is proud to welcome @saramwinter to our roster!

Sara Winter is currently building a promising career in the world of #golf as she transitions from Amateur to Pro status. A former Miss Canada and pageant queen, Sara personifies elegance on the course with unparalleled form and drive.

Next, Sara will compete in events across the Women’s All Pro Tour (WAPT) and Cactus Tour, with plans to also compete in the LPGA’s Q-School/Series ahead of joining the Epson Tour, the official development golf tour of the LPGA Tour.

We are so proud to have Sara join the Dulcedo family!

i like my pre shot routine short & simple,hbu? 

••let’s talk mental game— we all want to get better at golf, so we need to work on the most important club, the one between our ears. That’s where @golfguruapp comes in.

I’ve been testing out this app for a month now & I’m blown away. I tend to lose focus very easily or overthink, golf guru has helped make the game more fun & simple. 

Link in bio to download & try free sessions, use code: SARA_1MF - let me know what you think, I feel really passionate ab this & I hope y’all will give it a try. 🫶🏼🥹🧠🏌🏽‍♀️☮️✨
